Package com.github.astefanich.exchange

Classes to provide functionality of a ExchangeAdapter and StockExchange through a network connection.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExchangeNetworkAdapter
    Provides a network adapter for a StockExchange, which functions as our server application.
    ExchangeNetworkAdapterFactory
    Implementation class of NetworkExchangeAdapterFactory; creates instances of ExchangeNetworkAdapter.
    ExchangeNetworkProxy
    Client-side class for interacting with a network accessible StockExchange, which is accessed via a ExchangeNetworkAdapter.
    ExchangeNetworkProxyFactory
    Factory implementation for creating instances of ExchangeNetworkProxy
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ProtocolConstants
    String/Integer constants for StockExchange commands being sent over the network, which composes the exchange protcol.
